st ./pkg/store/... -v` — all unit tests pass\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Dependencies\n37: \n38: - `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n39: - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n40: - `k8s.io/klog/v2`\n41: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` (to be verified/created)\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## References\n46: \n47: - Design: `session-store/design.md`\n48: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md`\n\n(End of file - total 48 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Interface & Errors\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/store/store.go` — define `Store` interface with all 9 methods per design spec\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/store/errors.go` — define `ErrNotFound` error variable\n- [ ] **1.3** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Implementation\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/store/singleton.go` — implement `Storage()`, `initStore()`, provider constants, singleton pattern","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775851468105,"end":1775851468117}}}}
