{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775851494633,"sessionID":"ses_28701628affeS0qakidQlEC2g4","part":{"id":"prt_d78ff1422001DteJbbLaRdV0vz","messageID":"msg_d78fef584001QuUK1vXYLQ4c8K","sessionID":"ses_28701628affeS0qakidQlEC2g4","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_7882aa1f74bc44f18d7a311a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Implementation Verification\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Verify `redisStore` struct defined in `pkg/store/store_redis.go` with fields: `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n- [ ] **1.2** Verify constants defined: `sessionKeyPrefix = \"session:\"`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey = \"session:expiry\"`, `sessionLastActivityKey = \"session:last_activity\"`\n- [ ] **1.3** Verify `makeRedisOptions()` parses `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` from environment\n- [ ] **1.4** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Basic Operations\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Verify `Ping(ctx)` executes `cli.Ping(ctx)` and expects string response \"PONG\"\n- [ ] **2.2** Verify `Ping` returns error on disconnected server\n- [ ] **2.3** Verify `GetSandboxBySessionID` uses GET and returns `ErrNotFound` for redis.Nil\n- [ ] **2.4** Verify `Close()` calls `cli.Close()` and returns any error\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: StoreSandbox Atomicity\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Verify `StoreSandbox` uses pipeline with SETNX, ZADD expiry, ZADD last_activity\n- [ ] **3.2** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates nil sandbox — returns error \"sandbox is nil\"\n- [ ] **3.3** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates zero ExpiresAt — returns error \"invalid expiry: ExpiresAt is zero\"\n- [ ] **3.4** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates empty SessionID — returns error \"session ID is required\"\n- [ ] **3.5** Verify ZSET scores: expiry uses `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, last activity uses `time.Now().Unix()`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: UpdateSandbox\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Verify `UpdateSandbox` uses SET with XX flag (NOT SetNX per delta-spec)\n- [ ] **4.2** Verify `UpdateSandbox` fails with error when key does not exist\n- [ ] **4.3** Verify `UpdateSandbox` does NOT modify expiry or last-activity ZSETs\n- [ ] **4.4** Fix implementation if using SetNX instead of SET with XX flag\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: DeleteSandbox\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Verify `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` uses pipeline with DEL and ZREM (both indices)\n- [ ] **5.2** Verify deletion succeeds for non-existent session (DEL returns 0, ZREM returns 0)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: List Operations\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Verify `ListExpiredSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on `session:expiry` index\n- [ ] **6.2** Verify `ListInactiveSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on `session:last_activity` index\n- [ ] **6.3** Verify both list operations return `nil, nil` when limit <= 0\n- [ ] **6.4** Verify list operations use MGet (pipeline) to load JSON for each session ID\n- [ ] **6.5** Verify orphan ZSET members (session ID in index but no session key) are skipped gracefully\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: UpdateSessionLastActivity\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Verify `UpdateSessionLastActivity` verifies key existence first via EXISTS\n- [ ] **7.2** Verify returns `ErrNotFound` when session key does not exist\n- [ ] **7.3** Verify uses `time.Now()` when timestamp is zero\n- [ ] **7.4** Verify rejects empty session ID with error\n- [ ] **7.5** Verify ZADD uses provided timestamp as score\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` — unit tests with mock Redis\n- [ ] **8.2** Verify `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` passes\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md` (Store interface)\n- Design: `session-store/design.md`\n- Spec: `session-store/spec.md`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/work